## ğŸ’¾ Save System

Your progress is automatically saved in your browser's local storage. Progress includes:
- Highest level reached
- Achievements unlocked
- Story progression
- Coins collected
- Personal leaderboard

âš ï¸ **Note:** Progress is stored locally. Clearing browser cache will reset your save.

